{"tid":1756341,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一句講曬，裝唔裝修 砵蘭街勝和d雞竇 ?????","createTime":"2019-11-26T03:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T08:59:02.000Z","uid":222970,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"868594542c13da2b83db11f30b2b003c3254e9a4","tid":1756341,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cG0ka11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcG0ka11.jpg&h=4c28469d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHA8jVm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHA8jVm.jpg&h=25b7ce9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRy56An.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRy56An.jpg&h=f7155c36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NyrrQ13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNyrrQ13.jpg&h=e81cf9e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有江湖人士跟本刊透露，這幾名拿著斧頭的惡男，有黑幫水房背景。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其中穿著黑色西裝高舉斧頭的男士，原來叫做浩南</span></span>，有古惑仔為他起了個花名叫「砵蘭街浩南哥」。這個拿著斧頭的砵蘭街浩南哥並不是話事人，只是在砵蘭街經營指壓場靠妓女維生的古惑佬。有人估計，因為抗爭活動影響到砵蘭街的淫業生意，所以古惑佬就乘機找威者出氣。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>浩南哥在砵蘭街活躍多年，是花朵「彪頭」的水房大佬的門生。而水房在砵蘭街一帶有三股勢力，經營指壓場的以「彪頭」為代表人物</strong></span></span>。彪頭在砵蘭街打滾20多年，具有江湖地位。而彪頭主力經營指壓場，十多年前好景時坐擁達十多間，很多社團兄弟都跟佢搵食。而彪頭的指壓場特點是較少用持旅遊證件入境的北姑，多數都是用有身份證的新移民，減低被查牌風險。<br />\n<br />\n而另一批是經營夜總會的，當中代表人物是一名叫「憤超」的水房大佬，砵蘭街內凡是金字頭的夜總會，憤超都有份投資。另外，砵蘭街內的瑞興麻雀館和附近瑞字頭的麻雀館，都是水房人馬開設，更是最賺錢的一門生意。<br />\n<br />\n其實砵蘭街的古惑仔襲擊示威者，較早前已有前科。本月初凌晨，一批示威者去到旺角砵蘭街時，亦被多名黑幫古惑仔恐嚇推撞。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>仲有旺角間瑞興麻雀館</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KgqsAx0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKgqsAx0.png&h=32c30b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yThXMn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yThXMn.png&h=322d876e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb4da0259ca387b8b08fbfcff4180132138299c3","tid":1756341,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:52:08.000Z","msg":"文寫水房喎"},{"pid":"15e1196eb1a2cd62583e8bc386f2eea2b76f035e","tid":1756341,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:53:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>建議裝修 先下手為強 上次拎斧頭恐嚇手足唔使付出代價啊？建議下次油尖旺有大型示威先幫佢裝修 等到我地多人先搞 今次唔搞佢 下次我地就有手足俾佢斬死</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"466a585270e0880f3b42c0d2c34e9218dda2562f","tid":1756341,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb4da0259ca387b8b08fbfcff4180132138299c3","tid":1756341,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:52:08.000Z","msg":"文寫水房喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:53:42.000Z","msg":"屌 搞錯 我重po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5f2470cc74c5dd2adecb52ea2963c4f022adda","tid":1756341,"uid":25721,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"唔好啦， 人地有刀手"},{"pid":"0a50aac5c48f3ed93b0edb34cd800443228b4285","tid":1756341,"uid":316537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:54:48.000Z","msg":"OK 你想點懲罰佢地"},{"pid":"003f0ea5d9d353d914feebecb9f9a64879eff538","tid":1756341,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"扯皮條靠女人做雞皮肉錢維生既浩南哥下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4444bb80eea652eada805ba19209add62654a918","tid":1756341,"uid":221004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb5f2470cc74c5dd2adecb52ea2963c4f022adda","tid":1756341,"uid":25721,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"唔好啦， 人地有刀手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20